name: Onlooking
description: I was perusing around Portsmouth Square a hole in the wall destination where most of the men in Chinatown play Mahjong I caught a very vulnerable moment by one of the homeless men looking out into the street for what it seems to be immersing himself in remembrance of what it was like to be once apart of society and in the same essence forgotten while foraging for resources to sustain himself I hope that in my heart that he's well and thriving. - San Francisco; April 23,2019
